# Runtime state — never commit these to git.
# Committing them causes conflicts and accidental state changes when merging/rebasing.
#
# Tracked files (shared project knowledge): decisions.md, gotchas.md, tech-debt.md
# Everything else is ephemeral per-session state.

# Unsupervised mode flag + usage threshold
settings.md

# Session checkpoints (branch-scoped and legacy root)
context.md
context-*.md

# Headless auto-start marker (written by claude-loop.sh before each headless session)
auto-start.marker

# Usage guard runtime markers
*.active

# Cached API rate-limit data (refreshed each session)
usage-cache.json

# Unsupervised mode session log
*.log
